title: Chiefs-Patriots & Packers- Falcons Recap, Houston Fires Bill O'Brien, and TNF Week 5 Preview
itunes:title: Chiefs-Patriots & Packers- Falcons Recap, Houston Fires Bill O'Brien, and TNF Week 5 Preview
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, and Gregg Rosenthal are joined by Patrick Claybon to recap the two Monday night games. The Chiefs won, but the quarterback play in New England is the main topic of discussion (2:40). Aaron Rodgers is on fire, but not the same way some of the Atlanta players and staff might be under (10:59). Seth Payne stops by to discuss the Texans and the latest Bill O'Brien news (21:47) and the heroes preview the TNF matchup between the Bears and the Bucs (38:52)
